engChrName: Hah! I'll teach ya to look down on my baby!
engSearchText: Hah! I'll teach ya to look down on my baby!
jpnChrName: ハッ、これが全開だと思うなよッ！
jpnSearchText: ハッ、これが全開だと思うなよッ！

engChrName: Eat my dust!
engSearchText: Eat my dust!
jpnChrName: ここで差を付けるッ！
jpnSearchText: ここで差を付けるッ！

engChrName: Can't corner at that speed, rookie!
engSearchText: Can't corner at that speed, rookie!
jpnChrName: フッ、スピード出し過ぎなのさ！
jpnSearchText: フッ、スピード出し過ぎなのさ！

engChrName: I've got two little helpers that beg to differ!
engSearchText: I've got two little helpers that beg to differ!
jpnChrName: 育ち盛りが２人いりゃあ、 何とかなんだろッ！
jpnSearchText:
育ち盛りが２人いりゃあ、
何とかなんだろッ！

engChrName: Yeah!
engSearchText: Yeah!
jpnChrName: っしゃあ！
jpnSearchText: っしゃあ！

engChrName: Hold on!
engSearchText: Hold on!
jpnChrName: あっぶねえ！
jpnSearchText: あっぶねえ！

engChrName: How the hell...?!
engSearchText: How the hell...?!
jpnChrName: なぜ曲がれる！？
jpnSearchText: なぜ曲がれる！？

engChrName: I see... Their weight stabilized his turn!
engSearchText: I see... Their weight stabilized his turn!
jpnChrName: そうか、あの子たちの 荷重を利用したのか！？
jpnSearchText:
そうか、あの子たちの
荷重を利用したのか！？

engChrName: Eyes on the road, champ!
engSearchText: Eyes on the road, champ!
jpnChrName: よそ見すんなよ、チャンピオン！
jpnSearchText: よそ見すんなよ、チャンピオン！

engChrName: Let's go!
engSearchText: Let's go!
jpnChrName: うおおおおおっ！！
jpnSearchText: うおおおおおっ！！

engChrName: That was close...
engSearchText: That was close...
jpnChrName: ギリギリか……！
jpnSearchText: ギリギリか……！

engChrName: Comin' through!
engSearchText: Comin' through!
jpnChrName: すまん、通るぜ！
jpnSearchText: すまん、通るぜ！

engChrName: What?!
engSearchText: What?!
jpnChrName: そんな……！？
jpnSearchText: そんな……！？

engChrName: Still stuck back there? Don't think he'd try off-roading in a sports car.
engSearchText:
Still stuck back there? Don't think he'd try
off-roading in a sports car.
jpnChrName: 減速したか車道を外れたか……
jpnSearchText: 減速したか車道を外れたか……

engChrName: Lame. Didn't think he'd give up so easy.
engSearchText: Lame. Didn't think he'd give up so easy.
jpnChrName: ケツについてくるかと思ったが 案外諦めるのが早かったな。
jpnSearchText:
ケツについてくるかと思ったが
案外諦めるのが早かったな。

engChrName: You're kidding me!
engSearchText: You're kidding me!
jpnChrName: 嘘だろ……！？
jpnSearchText: 嘘だろ……！？

engChrName: Miss me?
engSearchText: Miss me?
jpnChrName: やあ、元気だったかい？
jpnSearchText: やあ、元気だったかい？

engChrName: Crazy bastard weaved between the buses!
engSearchText: Crazy bastard weaved between the buses!
jpnChrName: こいつ……バスを全部 躱して来たっていうのかよ？
jpnSearchText:
こいつ……バスを全部
躱して来たっていうのかよ？

engChrName: Earned
engSearchText: Earned
jpnChrName: ＳＰが上がった。
jpnSearchText: ＳＰが<C2><C0>上がった。

engChrName: Putting up more of a fight than I expected.
engSearchText: Putting up more of a fight than I expected.
jpnChrName: 確かにいいマシンだ、テクも悪くない。
jpnSearchText: 確かにいいマシンだ、テクも悪くない。

engChrName: But your fate was sealed the moment you decided to cross the great Maxim Lugan!
engSearchText:
But your fate was sealed the moment you decided to
cross the great Maxim Lugan!
jpnChrName: ただ運だけは悪いようだ── 何せ相手はこの《紅い流星（マクシム・ルーガン）》だからなッ！
jpnSearchText:
ただ運だけは悪いようだ──
何せ相手はこの《紅い流星（マクシム・ルーガン）》だからなッ！

engChrName: Guess he ain't a pro for nothing.
engSearchText: Guess he ain't a pro for nothing.
jpnChrName: ……流石は本職、抜ける隙はねえか。
jpnSearchText: ……流石は本職、抜ける隙はねえか。

engChrName: Time to bust out my ace in the hole!
engSearchText: Time to bust out my ace in the hole!
jpnChrName: だったら裏技を使わせてもらうぜ。 こんくらいはハンデとは言わねえよな！？
jpnSearchText:
だったら裏技を使わせてもらうぜ。
こんくらいはハンデとは言わねえよな！？

engChrName: Is that a turbocharger?! Those things are brand new!
engSearchText: Is that a turbocharger?! Those things are brand new!
jpnChrName: ターボチャージャー！？ ワークスで開発されたばかりの！
jpnSearchText:
ターボチャージャー！？
ワークスで開発されたばかりの！

engChrName: Haha! This is getting interesting! I'll just have to—!
engSearchText: Haha! This is getting interesting! I'll just have to—!
jpnChrName: ハハッ、面白い！ こうなったらとことん──
jpnSearchText:
ハハッ、面白い！
こうなったらとことん──

jpnChrName: なっ！！？
jpnSearchText: なっ！！？

engChrName: Shit!
engSearchText: Shit!

engChrName: ...Are the foxes all right?
engSearchText: ...Are the foxes all right?
jpnChrName: ……さっきの狐たちは？
jpnSearchText: ……さっきの狐たちは？

engChrName: It looks like they got away safely.
engSearchText: It looks like they got away safely.
jpnChrName: えと…… 車道の外に逃げたみたいです。
jpnSearchText:
えと……
車道の外に逃げたみたいです。

engChrName: I suppose monsters aren't the only creatures that cause accidents...
engSearchText:
I suppose monsters aren't the only creatures that
cause accidents...
jpnChrName: 魔獣以外にも、野生動物の事故は 結構あるみたいですね……
jpnSearchText:
魔獣以外にも、野生動物の事故は
結構あるみたいですね……

engChrName: Let's hope they've learned their lesson to stay off the road.
engSearchText:
Let's hope they've learned their lesson to stay off
the road.
jpnChrName: これに懲りて、もう二度と車道に 入らなければいいんですけど……
jpnSearchText:
これに懲りて、もう二度と車道に
入らなければいいんですけど……

engChrName: Right...
engSearchText: Right...
jpnChrName: そうか……
jpnSearchText: そうか……

engChrName: Tough break, huh?
engSearchText: Tough break, huh?
jpnChrName: なんつーか、災難だったな。
jpnSearchText: なんつーか、災難だったな。

engChrName: Hmph. I don't need your pity. You and your Ingert won.
engSearchText:
Hmph. I don't need your pity. You and your
Ingert won.
jpnChrName: フン……勝負は勝負、 君とインゲルトの勝ちだ。
jpnSearchText:
フン……勝負は勝負、
君とインゲルトの勝ちだ。

engChrName: Come on now—
engSearchText: Come on now—
jpnChrName: いや、あれは──
jpnSearchText: いや、あれは──

engChrName: When a car goes off course, the driver bears the responsibility. That's the rule.
engSearchText:
When a car goes off course, the driver bears
the responsibility. That's the rule.
jpnChrName: コースアウトはそいつの責任、 それがレースだ。
jpnSearchText:
コースアウトはそいつの責任、
それがレースだ。

engChrName: You all can go. The engine's fine, and I can handle her basic repairs myself.
engSearchText:
You all can go. The engine's fine, and I can handle
her basic repairs myself.
jpnChrName: 駆動系に問題はないから行きたまえ。 簡単な修理なら僕一人でもできる。
jpnSearchText:
駆動系に問題はないから行きたまえ。
簡単な修理なら僕一人でもできる。

engChrName: If anything comes up, give me a call.
engSearchText: If anything comes up, give me a call.
jpnChrName: ま、何かあれば連絡しな。
jpnSearchText: ま、何かあれば連絡しな。

engChrName: I feel kind of sorry for him...
engSearchText: I feel kind of sorry for him...
jpnChrName: ちょっと気の毒でしたね……
jpnSearchText: ちょっと気の毒でしたね……

engChrName: Me, too. I didn't think he'd accept defeat like that.
engSearchText: Me, too. I didn't think he'd accept defeat like that.
jpnChrName: はい……素直に 負けを認めたのも意外でした。
jpnSearchText:
はい……素直に
負けを認めたのも意外でした。

engChrName: Stuff like that is what makes you a champ.
engSearchText: Stuff like that is what makes you a champ.
jpnChrName: ヤツもあくまでレーサーってことだろ。
jpnSearchText: ヤツもあくまでレーサーってことだろ。

engChrName: Heh. Maybe he's got some good in him after all.
engSearchText: Heh. Maybe he's got some good in him after all.
jpnChrName: ま……少しくらいはこっちの ロマンに応えてもらわねえとな。
jpnSearchText:
ま……少しくらいはこっちの
ロマンに応えてもらわねえとな。

engChrName: After all that racing, we should get into Langport on time.
engSearchText:
After all that racing, we should get into Langport
on time.
jpnChrName: 差し引きゼロのペースだ── このままラングポートを目指すぞ。
jpnSearchText:
差し引きゼロのペースだ──
このままラングポートを目指すぞ。

engChrName: Nice job keepin' pace...
engSearchText: Nice job keepin' pace...
jpnChrName: ついてくるじゃねえか、女ライダー。
jpnSearchText: ついてくるじゃねえか、女ライダー。

engChrName: ...but the real match starts here!
engSearchText: ...but the real match starts here!
jpnChrName: そろそろアウトバーンの中じゃ かなり急なカーブが来る──
jpnSearchText:
そろそろアウトバーンの中じゃ
かなり急なカーブが来る──

engChrName: Try not to eat pavement on this turn.
engSearchText: Try not to eat pavement on this turn.
jpnChrName: 振り落とされるんじゃねえぜ？
jpnSearchText: 振り落とされるんじゃねえぜ？

engChrName: How about you try not to eat my dust?
engSearchText: How about you try not to eat my dust?
jpnChrName: あなたの方こそ、遅れないでよね？
jpnSearchText: あなたの方こそ、遅れないでよね？

engChrName: Man, she's jacking up her speed before a corner like this? That takes balls!
engSearchText:
Man, she's jacking up her speed before a corner
like this? That takes balls!
jpnChrName: ハッ、このカーブに加速して入るだと！？ おもしれえ！
jpnSearchText:
ハッ、このカーブに加速して入るだと！？
おもしれえ！

engChrName: Man, she's not slowin' down even before a corner like this? That takes balls!
engSearchText:
Man, she's not slowin' down even before a corner
like this? That takes balls!
jpnChrName: ハッ、このカーブでも減速しねえだと？ おもしれえ！
jpnSearchText:
ハッ、このカーブでも減速しねえだと？
おもしれえ！

engChrName: She sped up THERE?!
engSearchText: She sped up THERE?!
jpnChrName: あそこでさらに加速かよ！
jpnSearchText: あそこでさらに加速かよ！

engChrName: Lady's got one crazy sense of balance, don't she?
engSearchText: Lady's got one crazy sense of balance, don't she?
jpnChrName: いやいや、どんなバランス感覚してんだ！？
jpnSearchText: いやいや、どんなバランス感覚してんだ！？

engChrName: That was amazing! It takes real skills and an amazing bike to pull that off.
engSearchText:
That was amazing! It takes real skills and an amazing
bike to pull that off.
jpnChrName: わぁ～！　エルメスさんの技術と、 バイクの加速力があってこそのワザだね！
jpnSearchText:
わぁ～！　エルメスさんの技術と、
バイクの加速力があってこそのワザだね！

engChrName: Hahaha! Not bad!
engSearchText: Hahaha! Not bad!
jpnChrName: クハハ、やるじゃねえか！！
jpnSearchText: クハハ、やるじゃねえか！！

engChrName: Hyaaa!
engSearchText: Hyaaa!
jpnChrName: はああああっ！！
jpnSearchText: はああああっ！！

engChrName: Bah. Lost by the skin of my teeth.
engSearchText: Bah. Lost by the skin of my teeth.
jpnChrName: チッ、ハナ差で負けたか……
jpnSearchText: チッ、ハナ差で負けたか……

engChrName: Phew... That was a close one.
engSearchText: Phew... That was a close one.
jpnChrName: ふぅ……何とかなったわね。
jpnSearchText: ふぅ……何とかなったわね。

engChrName: Hahaha! Not bad!
engSearchText: Hahaha! Not bad!
jpnChrName: クハハ、やるじゃねえか！！
jpnSearchText: クハハ、やるじゃねえか！！

engChrName: Hyaaa!
engSearchText: Hyaaa!
jpnChrName: はああああっ！！
jpnSearchText: はああああっ！！

engChrName: *pant* That was down to the wire.
engSearchText: *pant* That was down to the wire.
jpnChrName: ハァハァ……危なかったぜ……
jpnSearchText: ハァハァ……危なかったぜ……

engChrName: Tch. And I was so close, too...
engSearchText: Tch. And I was so close, too...
jpnChrName: あと少し……悔しいわね。
jpnSearchText: あと少し……悔しいわね。

engChrName: Now!
engSearchText: Now!
jpnChrName: ここよ──！
jpnSearchText: ここよ──！
